text: Tamás Wichmann (4 February 1948 – 12 February 2020) was a Hungarian sprint canoeist. He competed from 1966 to 1983. Wichmann competed in four Summer Olympics, he won three medals. This included two silver (C-1 1000 m: 1972, C-2 1000 m: 1968) and one bronze (C-1 1000 m: 1976). ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1948 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympic silver medalists for Hungary Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Hungary Category:Canoeists
